"betaValue\");\n+        } finally {\n+            Context.exit();\n+        }\n+    }\n+\n+    private static ShellConsole createJLineV1Console(Scriptable scope, Charset charset) throws Exception {\n+        Method factory = ShellConsole.class.getDeclaredMethod(\n+                \"getJLineShellConsoleV1\",\n+                ClassLoader.class,\n+                Class.class,\n+                Scriptable.class,\n+                Charset.class);\n+        factory.setAccessible(true);\n+        return (ShellConsole) factory.invoke(\n+                null,\n+                ShellConsole.class.getClassLoader(),\n+                jline.ConsoleReader.class,\n+                scope,\n+                charset);\n+    }\n+\n     private static String readConsoleInput(InputStream in) throws IOException {\n         byte[] buffer = new byte[64];\n         int read = in.read(buffer);\ndiff --git a/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/proxy-config.json b/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/proxy-config.json\nindex b2bd6cfdc..fc3eddb8e 100644\n--- a/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/proxy-config.json\n+++ b/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/proxy-config.json\n@@ -1,4 +1,7 @@\n [\n+  [\n+    \"jline.Completor\"\n+  ],\n   [\n     \"jline.console.completer.Completer\"\n   ]\ndiff --git a/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/reflect-config.json b/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/reflect-config.json\nindex eeee998fb..b3f61a8bc 100644\n--- a/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/reflect-config.json\n+++ b/tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/reflect-config.json\n@@ -1,4 +1,59 @@\n [\n+  {\n+    \"name\": \"jline.ConsoleReader\",\n+    \"allPublicConstructors\": true,\n+    \"methods\": [\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"addCompletor\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"jline.Completor\"\n+        ]\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"flushConsole\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": []\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"printNewline\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": []\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"printString\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"java.lang.String\"\n+        ]\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"readLine\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": []\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"readLine\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"java.lang.String\"\n+        ]\n+      },\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"setBellEnabled\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"boolean\"\n+        ]\n+      }\n+    ]\n+  },\n+  {\n+    \"name\": \"jline.Completor\",\n+    \"methods\": [\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"complete\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"java.lang.String\",\n+          \"int\",\n+          \"java.util.List\"\n+        ]\n+      }\n+    ]\n+  },\n   {\n     \"name\": \"jline.console.ConsoleReader\",\n     \"allPublicConstructors\": true,\n@@ -60,6 +115,20 @@\n       }\n     ]\n   },\n+  {\n+    \"name\": \"org.mozilla.javascript.tools.shell.ShellConsole\",\n+    \"methods\": [\n+      {\n+        \"name\": \"getJLineShellConsoleV1\",\n+        \"parameterTypes\": [\n+          \"java.lang.ClassLoader\",\n+          \"java.lang.Class\",\n+          \"org.mozilla.javascript.Scriptable\",\n+          \"java.nio.charset.Charset\"\n+        ]\n+      }\n+    ]\n+  },\n   {\n     \"name\": \"org_mozilla.rhino.JavaAdapterTest$JavaAdapterSelfHolder\",\n     \"fields\": [\n M tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/java/org_mozilla/rhino/ShellConsoleTest.java\n M tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/test/proxy-config.json\n M tests/src/org.mozilla/rhino/1.7R5/src/test